& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is LM Studio worker readiness profile integration
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_readiness_profile_001
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 0
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioReadinessProfile001] is the active semantic stack frame for the LM Studio readiness profile integration
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_readiness_profile_001
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is none
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_004, readiness_profile_008, lmstudio_next_probe_001, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is LMStudioWorkerFunctionalLane.sop, LMStudioAgentBenchmark.sop, lm_studio_worker_readiness_profile_20260624_008.sop, 2026-06-24_lmstudio_next_probe_result_001.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_004.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is integrated narrow readiness evidence for scratch-isolated LM Studio SOP proposal jobs
  + [question_register] is how to define diverse task-family evidence before raising readiness claims
  + [delineation_register] is inside readiness_profile, ready_surface, evidence_count, readiness_limits, next_gate, and profile_outside
  + [periphery_register] is same-family repetition, broad competence outside, project-root authority outside, validator gate, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is integrate_readiness_profile, update_lane_contract, emit_tick_004, update_reentry_state
  + [evidence_register] is readiness_profile_008, result_001, captured worker output 008, validation score 100, and operating_loop_tick_004
  + [wisdom_register] is narrow evidence should become a profile, not a broad claim
  + [caution_register] is repeated same-family score 100 does not prove broad task competence or project-root authority
  + [balance_register] is stable because readiness limits and outside are explicitly preserved
  + [integration_register] is pending commit, push, and diversified task corpus definition
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, broad local-worker readiness, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

(current_attention_runtime_registry_state) :active_root_frame: /semantic_register_set and return_anchor/ |registry_outside|
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_readiness_profile_001
  + [semantic_register_set] is focus, question, delineation, periphery, operation, evidence, Wisdom, Caution, balance, and integration registers
  + [return_anchor] is CurrentFocalPoint
  |registry_outside| hidden model state, executable runtime stack, unreviewed worker authority, unrelated dirty files, and untracked cognition

/ [CurrentFocalPoint], [AttentionRuntimeRegistry], [LMStudioWorkerFunctionalLane] -(EntersFrame)> [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioReadinessProfile001], [registry_outside]
* [semantic_register_set], [return_anchor], [frame_trace] -(SupportsReentry)> [readiness_profile], [operating_loop_tick], [balance_register], [integration_register], [outside]
